Package: libclamav-client-perl
Architecture: all
Depends: ${perl:Depends}, liberror-perl, ${misc:Depends}
Suggests: clamav-daemon
Description: A client class for the ClamAV `clamd` virus scanner daemon
 ClamAV::Client is a class acting as a client for a ClamAV `clamd` virus
 scanner daemon.  The daemon may run locally or on a remote system as
 ClamAV::Client can use both Unix domain sockets and TCP/IP sockets.
 The full functionality of the `clamd` client/server protocol is supported.
